---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'TikTok — Demetri Williams',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-6 py-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">TikTok</h1>
    <p class="text-muted mb-3">
      I document my life as a Computer Science student at LSU — covering projects, study tips, campus life, and everything in between.
    </p>
    <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@himdemetrii" target="_blank" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium text-lg">@himdemetrii →</a>

    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="border border-gray-700/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-1">34K+</p>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm">Followers</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-gray-700/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Lifestyle</p>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm">Content Focus</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-gray-700/50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-1">LSU</p>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm">Campus Life</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 mb-8 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">What I Create</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">I built my audience by documenting the real experience of being a Computer Science major — the late nights, the breakthroughs, the projects, and the grind. My content covers day-in-the-life vlogs, CS study motivation, project breakdowns, and college life at LSU. I've used TikTok's analytics tools to track engagement, retention, follower growth, and content performance to continuously refine my strategy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-8 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Brand Collaborations</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">My growth and engagement have led to collaborations with high-profile brands including DoorDash, Versace, Niche, and others. These partnerships have strengthened my skills in content creation, brand communication, and digital analytics.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-8 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Analytics & Strategy</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">I actively monitor content performance metrics including user engagement, retention rates, follower growth, and audience reach. These insights inform my posting strategy and help me identify high-performing content patterns to maximize impact.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      
        href="https://www.tiktok.com/@himdemetrii"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-accent hover:underline font-semibold text-lg"
      >
        View My TikTok Profile →
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>
</Layout>